{
  "openapi": "3.0.1",
  "info": {
    "title": "文件存储服务 API",
    "description": "WisePen 文件上传、下载、删除与回调接口",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://172.28.0.13:19907",
      "description": "Generated server url"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "文件存储",
      "description": "用户文件与图片上传代理接口"
    },
    {
      "name": "外部 - 文件存储",
      "description": "处理云存储服务回调"
    },
    {
      "name": "内部 - 文件存储",
      "description": "供业务微服务初始化上传、获取下载地址与管理物理文件"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/storage/imageUpload": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["文件存储"],
        "summary": "上传图床图片",
        "description": "- 用途：代理当前用户上传小尺寸图片并生成可访问的存储记录。\n- 请求：file 为图片文件；scene 指定图片存储场景；bizTag 为业务隔离目录标识，可为空。\n- 约束：当前用户必须已登录；文件扩展名只能是 jpg、jpeg、png、gif 或 webp；scene 只能属于用户公开图片、小组公开图片或笔记私有图片场景；文件大小不能超过小文件代理上传上限。\n- 处理：校验文件类型和场景后直接上传到主存储配置，创建 AVAILABLE 状态的存储记录；不走预签名直传和上传完成回调流程。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN；文件类型不支持 -> FileStorageError.CANNOT_SUPPORT_FILE_TYPE；场景不支持 -> FileStorageError.CANNOT_SUPPORT_FILE_STORAGE_SCENE；文件过大 -> FileStorageError.FILE_SIZE_ABOVE_UPPER_BOUND；存储上传失败 -> FileStorageError.STORAGE_PROVIDER_UPLOAD_FILE_FAILED。\n- 响应：返回存储记录、objectKey 和访问域名信息。\n",
        "operationId": "uploadImageProxy",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "scene",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "default": "true",
              "enum": [
                "PUBLIC_IMAGE_FOR_USER",
                "PUBLIC_IMAGE_FOR_GROUP",
                "PRIVATE_IMAGE_FOR_NOTE",
                "PRIVATE_DOC",
                "PRIVATE_SKILL_ASSET"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "bizTag",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "required": ["file"],
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "file": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "binary"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RStorageRecordDTO"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/external/storage/callback/upload": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["外部 - 文件存储"],
        "summary": "接收上传完成回调",
        "description": "- 用途：接收对象存储服务在直传文件完成后的服务端回调。\n- 请求：rawBody 携带 objectKey、md5 和 size 等回调参数；请求头携带云厂商签名信息。\n- 约束：回调必须通过存储提供方签名校验；objectKey 必须对应已初始化的上传记录。\n- 处理：校验签名后更新文件记录为 AVAILABLE，写入 md5 和文件大小，并发布文件上传完成事件；重复回调会被识别并忽略。\n- 失败：回调签名非法 -> FileStorageError.STORAGE_PROVIDER_CALLBACK_SIGNATURE_INVALID；文件记录缺失或回调参数异常导致未处理失败 -> CommonError.INTERNAL_ERROR。\n- 响应：成功时返回云厂商约定的 JSON 字符串。\n",
        "operationId": "handleUploadCallback",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "string"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "string"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": []
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "schemas": {
      "RStorageRecordDTO": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "key": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "msg": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "data": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/StorageRecordDTO"
          }
        }
      },
      "StorageRecordDTO": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "objectKey": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "md5": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "size": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          },
          "fileId": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          },
          "domain": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "securitySchemes": {
      "FromSource": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "内部来源校验头。直连微服务测试时填写 APISIX 注入的固定来源值。",
        "name": "X-From-Source",
        "in": "header"
      },
      "UserID": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "当前用户 ID。直连微服务测试 @CheckLogin 接口时手工模拟 APISIX 注入。",
        "name": "X-User-Id",
        "in": "header"
      },
      "IdentityType": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "当前用户身份类型：1=学生，2=教师，3=管理员。",
        "name": "X-Identity-Type",
        "in": "header"
      },
      "GroupRoleMap": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "当前用户小组角色 JSON，例如 {\"10001\":0}，角色值：0=OWNER，1=ADMIN，2=MEMBER。",
        "name": "X-Group-Role-Map",
        "in": "header"
      }
    }
  }
}
